{"tid":739230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"挪威諾貝爾委員會：繼續邀請劉霞替丈夫領獎","createTime":"2018-07-12T03:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T03:17:54.000Z","uid":70063,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"099956956dfe8ee30f5f5cb17d9f3eddc7da3934","tid":739230,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T03:10:26.000Z","msg":"挪威諾貝爾委員會主席發表聲明，就2010年和平獎得主劉曉波的遺孀劉霞，可以如願離開中國表示安慰，並會繼續邀請她到奧斯陸代替丈夫領獎。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，中國政府決定終止對劉霞不公的壓迫是好事，但她所受的非人道對待從不應該發生。委員會對劉曉波夫婦在中國就人權與自由作出的努力，致以最深的感謝，並指他們的犧牲，將會惠及全中國人民。<br />\n<br />\n委員會亦對德國總理默克爾及德國政府，對劉曉波及劉霞的不懈支持表示感謝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406348-20180711.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406348-20180711.htm&d=3l4Hg6ZQgzo2poxeTVxz%2B9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=ccfa3d6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1406348-20180711.htm&h=bc5e47bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1406348-20180711.htm</a>"},{"pid":"46c18134e7d5c64960a1f29e491e8499a19a1088","tid":739230,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T03:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}